title: Could Miami Turn Red? with Rich Baris and Devin Nunes
itunes:title: Could Miami Turn Red? with Rich Baris and Devin Nunes
description:
Miami-Dade County one of America's most densely-populated counties, so it must be a permanent Democratic stronghold...or is it? Charlie speaks to polling guru Rich Baris about the possibility Miami will go red in November, and other signs of a coming GOP landslide. Plus, Charlie talks to former Congressman and Truth Social CEO Devin Nunes about how Truth has created an alternative online ecosystem without left-wing censorship.
